<p class="ql-align-center">董其昌跋米芾《蜀素帖》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“平淡天真”还体现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在他对用墨的讲究上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以淡墨作书</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以说是董其昌的一种创造</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200901/e68a3b8596b443498055a33684299cdd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
