<p class="ql-align-center">台北故宫博物院藏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/3fa6f8d67852486ba25e910d874bbd5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">董其昌论画册（局部）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在董其昌之前极少见到书家运用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晚于董其昌的书家王铎</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">创造了涨墨法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">利用墨的干湿来表现胸中的激情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但在墨的浓淡方面似无明显之变化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200901/f0301c3e7a994c7095ee7b1fd922ff61.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
